	<p pid="a.159.1/1">asked Her Majesty's Government:</p>
	<p pid="a.159.1/2" qnum="HL5545">Whether the 2.5 per cent. levy on underspending National Health Service trusts, designed to support those trusts that have overspent, will impact more on trusts which serve mainly (a) urban, or (b) rural areas; and whether the levies will apply to all trusts that have broken even or made a profit.</p>
